{"type": "article", "id": 38311, "title": "五线谱很窄，但是挤进去一张海报没什么问题｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-03-01T23:24:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 15397, "name": "Grovemade"}, {"id": 38136, "name": "People Too"}, {"id": 38137, "name": "Banale"}, {"id": 38138, "name": "BLOCD"}, {"id": 9226, "name": "Yves Béhar"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 321, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170301183909vpS0uJ2LxwBNbOjG.jpg", "contents": "<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>On Notes by Lena Erlich</h3><p>听到一首动人的旋律，你的脑海中或许会浮现出一个画面或是一段剧情。在一次无意的乐谱涂鸦之后，隶属于俄罗斯创意工作室 <a href=\"http://peopletoo.ru/\">People Too</a> 的 Lena Erlich 就用她的奇思妙想，把原先中规中矩的黑白乐谱变成了一幅幅生动有趣的画作。在 Erlich 的乐谱世界中，几乎每一个音符都有用武之地，成为道具的一部分或是人物的歇脚处。如果你对这些乐谱画感兴趣的话，可以通过<a href=\"https://www.artflakes.com/en/shop/peopletoo\">链接</a>购买，海报售价为 6.48 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170301183944TVH5mWt8wUD0SM13.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.398889\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170301183945512E7RV98rzBnAZM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.580000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170301183944w4NbtQpDBc9h361V.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.371111\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170301183945Kr7Hz1CmjWTo50kJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.323333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170301183945Lb5dX3RQcV8IlNZg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.337778\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170301183946i17qkATJM9aoSYvp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.326667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><h3>LOVE by Yves Béhar</h3><p>如果你留心过我们之前介绍的几款黑胶唱机，会发现这类产品大多以减轻播放门槛出发，主打便携性。最近，一支由知名产品设计师 Yves Béhar 领导的团队在此基础上，为唱片机添加了智能元素。这款名为 LOVE 的产品和我们之前介绍过的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/35775.html\">小木盒</a>一样，本身并不具备播放功能，但可以通过蓝牙、WiFi 或是音频线和扬声器相连。至于播放、暂停、音量和转速调节这类操作，它们都可以通过 LOVE 的触控表面或是配套的手机应用完成。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/493608538/love-the-worlds-first-intelligent-turntable\">链接</a>参与众筹，最低价为 369 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170301184004YyBdA8wJVzNjTarR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.733496\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201703011840048su0hl5PFn9ikvC1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.022005\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170301184004iVYUASCQ7Zn6gdho.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.733496\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170301221905aIqd5U2JgthfjM9O.gif\" data-ratio=\"0.559375\" data-format=\"gif\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170301221909ElgFvq0ScJ6RNsVz.gif\" data-ratio=\"0.559375\" data-format=\"gif\"> </figure></div><h3>Watch 02 by Grovemade &amp; Stefan Andrén</h3><p>以各类木制数码周边产品见长的美国设计品牌 <a href=\"https://grovemade.com/\">Grovemade</a> 最近又一次和前任耐克手表设计师 Stefan Andrén 合作，推出了 Watch 02 系列手表。它们延续了枫木/核桃木和皮革表带的组合，表面设计则一改 Watch 01 用镂空营造出的神秘感，采用了大大方方的常规表面，中间还有一圈微微的凹陷。这是它的<a href=\"https://grovemade.com/collections/wood-watch\">购买链接</a>，售价为 149 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170301184016BGsSRyEZWpXTYIeh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170301184016NcgEzseaHpX3x97h.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170301184016Vn47wqvPugMx8Tlh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201703011840179HP0h7lyaz4RLpGk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170301184017vPzFykNRLD0j9UZ7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><h3>Toothbrush by Banale</h3><p>洗漱品牌推出的旅行套装虽然方便，变小的牙刷和牙膏难免也会带来遗漏的隐忧。为此，意大利设计品牌 <a href=\"http://banale.com/\">Banale</a> 推出了一款将两者合二为一的洗漱工具。它采用折叠式设计，只要轻轻一推就能单独取出刷头，而内部的空间刚好可以容纳装有牙膏的小瓶。只要轻按按钮取出刷头，挤上牙膏再将它扣回顶部就可以开始刷牙了。这是它的<a href=\"http://banale.com/products/toothbrush.html\">购买链接</a>，售价为 15 欧元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170301184040boQ8S2RdIAYPgc3a.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170301184039woGcHZnXI01zvQOk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.692308\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170301184040y7WG6nKghxUDYc8S.png\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170301184039mWghrQsAkxICFXRq.png\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170301184039TVW5LREnhMkauyrp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.416667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><h3>Typesetting by BLOCD</h3><p>在去年的圣诞礼物季，西班牙创意机构 <a href=\"http://blocd.com/\">BLOCD</a> 为客户送去了一份和设计息息相关的礼物，一套制作成品牌 logo 活字的糖果。为了防止“误用”这些太过逼真的铅字，纸盒包装上还特别标注了 Typographic taste 的友情提示。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170301184240Di7VgPZu3y95Qbzw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.625000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170301184241v6GAECxhg0zHjqbK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.625000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170301184240kgLV2Rf87lDnBwUp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.625000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170301184240PSlrgFAUYh0senJw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.625000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><h3>Behind the Scene by Jojakim Cortis &amp; Adrian Sonderegger</h3><p>在今年的旧金山摄影展（<a href=\"http://www.photofairs.org/\">Photofairs</a>）上，来自瑞士的 <a href=\"http://www.ohnetitel.ch/\">Jojakim Cortis 和 Adrian Sonderegger</a> 通过这套名为 Behind the Scene 的作品构想了一个历史照片的“幕后世界”。他们自 2013 年起就开始通过微缩景观重现协和飞机失事、慕尼黑奥运会、长崎核弹爆炸等照片中的景观，提供另一种角度的解读。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170301184218UBK5oM3hczZQinvR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201703011842187wEblAHTgCP3sn2X.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667778\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170301184219zdhFrx4tOyvAD9qj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170301184218tI9mlWVseaX7iANp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201703011842198yVZ0m9rAQ3z17vw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images\" contenteditable=\"false\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" contenteditable=\"false\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170301184219Eo8VXabqg10FBmeC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div>"}